Broporo oooon duty! {{summoner:31}} 

That error might not be coming directly from Visual C++. It seems to me that the underlying issue might actually be a permissions issue. When the installer goes to pull on that file, your pc can block it entirely if you don't have the right settings in place. 

Check out our [**Permission Guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) to get those permission settings in place, and let me know if that helps!
